- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on word embeddings in NLP and document classification datasets. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a new framework for embedding distillation using ensemble learning. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper discusses deep learning and neural models. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is relevant as the paper focuses on neural models and their efficiency. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the transformation of word embeddings and their impact on accuracy.
